Question
========
What is the missing *F-value *of GROUP in the ANOVA table that is
presented below? Round to three decimals.  
  

  
![](Capture12333.gif)


Solution
========





SS<sub>M</sub> / *df*<sub>M</sub> = MS<sub>M</sub>  
SS<sub>R</sub> / *df*<sub>R</sub> = MS<sub>R</sub>  
MS<sub>M</sub> / MS<sub>R</sub> = *F*  
  
MS<sub>M</sub> = 5.624 / 3 = 1.875  
MS<sub>R</sub> = 57.695 / 95 = 0.607  
*F* = 1.875 / .607 = 3.089
